snippet.title: Palmyra Orphanage – Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Paranormal first-person horror, which takes place in an abandoned orphanage. Walk through the corridors of your childhood, but do remember that you're not the only one in here.


More information about our game you can find in our groups: 
Steam — https://store.steampowered.com/app/1085160/Palmyra_Orphanage/
VK - https://vk.com/steppe_hare 
We are supporting youtubers, streamers and other media. If you want to make content about our game, please send us letter with an attached link to your YouTube channel or other source on steppeharestudio@gmail.com. 


Music: 
NCBS “Horror Trailer Soundtrack" 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xCvWg9KqbvI
